ltivation%20traditionally%20sustained%20families.%20But%20he%20also%20recognised%20the%20need%20for%20diversification.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20to%20bring%20tourists%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%E2%80%99d%20explain%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20had%20to%20empower%20the%20people%20who%20called%20Koyna%20home.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20a%20partnership%20with%20local%20and%20state%20authorities%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CShama%20Prasad%20Mukherjee%20Jan%20Van%20Committee%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20transformative%20initiative%20spanning%2040%20villages%20in%20the%20Satara%20district.%20Each%20committee%20received%20a%20substantial%20grant%20of%2025%20lakh%20rupees%20for%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CForty%20percent%20of%20the%20funding%20was%20directed%20towards%20tourism%20infrastructure%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sangram%20detailed%2C%20%E2%80%9Cimproving%20viewpoints%2C%20reviving%20homestays%20and%20hotels%2C%20and%20giving%20restaurants%20a%20much-needed%20facelift.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20was%20immediate.%20Nikhil%20Mohite%2C%20a%20hotel%20owner%2C%20attested%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20when%20tourists%20came%20to%20Koyna%2C%20there%20was%20no%20decent%20place%20to%20stay%20and%20have%20a%20meal.%20Through%20the%20initiatives%20by%20Sangram%20and%20Discover%20Koyna%2C%20now%20a%20lot%20of%20small%20hotels%20and%20homestays%20have%20been%20revamped%20and%20all%20tourists%20stay%20at%20one%20of%20these%20places.%20This%20has%20not%20only%20given%20us%20a%20steady%20income%20but%20has%20improved%20the%20state%20of%20the%20hotels%20and%20restaurants%20in%20Koyna.%E2%80%9D%20Yogesh%20Desai%2C%20a%20newly%20trained%20forest%20g