20of%20a%20tour%20of%20over%2045%20days.%20On%20shorter%20tours%2C%20players%20can%20be%20accompanied%20by%20their%20families%20for%20up%20to%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20Innovation%20Lab%20Indian%20Sports%20Summit%20ahead%20of%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202025%2C%20Virat%20said%20as%20quoted%20by%20ESPNCricinfo%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20explain%20to%20people%20how%20grounding%20it%20is%20to%20just%20come%20back%20to%20your%20family%20every%20time%20you%20have%20something%20intense%2C%20which%20happens%20on%20the%20outside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20think%20people%20have%20an%20understanding%20of%20what%20value%20it%20brings%20to%20a%20large%20extent.%20And%20I%20feel%20quite%20disappointed%20about%20that%20because%20it%20is%20like%20people%20who%20have%20no%20control%20over%20what%20is%20going%20on%20are%20kind%20of%20brought%20into%20conversations%20and%20put%20out%20at%20the%20forefront%20that%2C%20'oh%2C%20maybe%20they%20need%20to%20be%20kept%20away'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20said%20that%20no%20player%20would%20like%20to%20%26quot%3Bsit%20alone%20and%20sulk%26quot%3B%20after%20a%20poor%20showing%20during%20a%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20be%20normal.%20And%20then%20you%20can%20really%20treat%20your%20game%20as%20something%20that%20is%20a%20responsibility.%20You%20finish%20that%20responsibility%2C%20and%20you%20come%20back%20to%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%2C%20there%20could%20be%20different%20situations%20happening%20in%20your%20life%20all%20the%20time.%20And%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20be%20absolutely%20normal.%20Not%20in%20a%20vague%20sense%2C%20but%20in%20a%20very%20real%20way%20that%20you%20finish%20your%20commitment%2C%20your%20responsibility%2C%20and%20then%20you%20come%20back%20to%20your%20house%2C%20you%20are%20with%20family%2C%20and%20there's%20absolutely%20normalcy%20in%20your%20house%20and%20normal%20family%20life%20goes%20on.%20So%2C%20for%20me%2C%20that%20is%20absolutely%20a%20day%20of%20immense%20pleasure.%20And%20I%20would%20not%20miss%20any%20opportunities%20to%20go%20out%20and%20spend%20time%20with%20my%20family%20whenever%20I%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Virat%20was%20a%20part%20of%20India's%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20winning%20team%20recently%2C%20emerging%20as%20the%20team's%20second-highest%20run-getter%20and%20overall%20fifth%2C%20with%20218%20runs%20in%20five%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2054.50.%20His%20standout%20knocks%20included%20a%20100*%20against%20arch-rivals%20Pakistan%20while%20chasing%20242%20and%20a%2098-ball%2084%20against%20Australia%20in%20the%20semifinals%20during%20a%20tough%20run-chase%20of%20265%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20be%20a%20part%20of%20RCB's%20IPL%202025%20season%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20tournament%20opener%20against%20defending%20champions%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20on%20March%2022%20at%20Eden%20Gardens%20in%20Kolkata.%20Not%20only%20would%20a%20maiden%20IPL%20title%20be%20on%20his%20target%2C%20but%20also%20plenty%20of%20batting%20records.%20He%20is%20the%20highest%20run-getter%20in%20tournament%20history%2C%20with%208%2C004%20runs%20in%20252%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2038.66%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20131.97%2C%20with%20eight%20centuries%20and%2055%20fifties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20he%20finished%20the%20season%20with%20an%20Orange%20Cap%20for%20most%20runs%2C%20with%20741%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2061.75%2C%20with%20an%20impressive%20strike%20rate%20of%20154.69.%20He%20scored%20a%20century%20and%20five%20fifties%20and%20hit%2038%20astonishing%20sixes.%20His%20team%20qualified%20for%20playoffs%20last%20season%20after%20a%20horror%20first%20half%20where%20they%20won%20just%20one%20match%20out%20of%20eight%2C%20following%20it%20wi