%20killed%20at%20least%2021%20people%2C%20the%20rebels%20said%20Sunday%2C%20as%20Washington%20warned%20Iran%20to%20stop%20backing%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Huthis%2C%20who%20have%20attacked%20Israel%20and%20Red%20Sea%20shipping%20throughout%20the%20Gaza%20war%2C%20said%20children%20were%20among%20those%20killed%20by%20the%20intense%20barrage%20of%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AFP%20photographer%20in%20the%20rebel-held%20capital%20Sanaa%20heard%20three%20explosions%20and%20saw%20plumes%20of%20smoke%20rising%20from%20a%20residential%20district%2C%20and%20strikes%20were%20also%20reported%20in%20Yemen's%20northern%20Saada%20region%2C%20a%20Huthi%20stronghold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNine%20civilians%20were%20killed%20and%20nine%20others%20were%20injured%2C%20most%20of%20them%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Huthis'%20health%20and%20environment%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20their%20Saba%20news%20agency%2C%20reporting%20the%20strikes%20on%20Sanaa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20strike%20in%20the%20Saada%20region%20killed%20at%20least%2010%20people%20and%20wounded%20others%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Huthi%20Ansarollah%20website%2C%20condemning%20what%20it%20called%20%26quot%3BUS-British%20aggression%26quot%3B%20and%20Washington's%20%26quot%3Bcriminal%20brutality%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20separate%20strike%20on%20a%20house%20in%20Saada's%20Alshaaf%20district%20killed%20two%20people%2C%20Ansarollah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Central%20Command%20(CENTCOM)%2C%20which%20posted%20images%20of%20fighters%20taking%20off%20from%20an%20aircraft%20carrier%20and%20a%20bomb%20demolishing%20a%20building%20compound%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Bprecision%20strikes%26quot%3B%20were%20launched%20to%20%26quot%3Bdefend%20American%20interests%2C%20deter%20enemies%2C%20and%20restore%20freedom%20of%20navigation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20immediate%20comment%20from%20British%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20social%20media%2C%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Buse%20overwhelming%20lethal%20force%20until%20we%20have%20achieved%20our%20objective%26quot%3B%2C%20citing%20the%20Huthis'%20threats%20against%20Red%20Sea%20shipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Escalation%20with%20escalation'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis%20vowed%20that%20the%20strikes%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20pass%20without%20response%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Yemeni%20armed%20forces%20are%20fully%20prepared%20to%20confront%20escalation%20with%20escalation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20rebels'%20political%20bureau%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20rebel%20Al-Masirah%20TV%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20warned%20Iran%20that%20it%20must%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%26quot%3B%20cut%20support%20to%20the%20Houthis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rebels%2C%20who%20have%20controlled%20much%20of%20Yemen%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20are%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Baxis%20of%20resistance%26quot%3B%20of%20pro-Iran%20groups%20staunchly%20opposed%20to%20Israel%20and%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20launched%20scores%20of%20drone%20and%20missile%20attacks%20at%20ships%20passing%20Yemen%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20during%20the%20Gaza%20war%2C%20claiming%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20campaign%20crippled%20the%20vital%20route%2C%20which%20normally%20carries%20about%2012%20percent%20of%20world%20shipping%20traffic%2C%20forcing%20many%20companies%20into%20a%20costly%20detour%20around%20southern%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas%2C%20grateful%20for%20the%20Houthi%20support%2C%20hit%20out%20Saturday%20at%20the%20US%20strikes%2C%20branding%20them%20%26quot%3Ba%20stark%20violation%20of%20international%20law%20and%20an%20assault%20on%20the%20country's%20sovereignty%20and%20stability%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Hell%20will%20rain%20down'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20launched%20several%20rounds%20of%20strikes%20on%20Houthi%20targets%2C%20some%20with%20British%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20halting%20their%20attacks%20when%20Gaza's%20ceasefire%20took%20effect%20in%20January%2C%20the%20Houthis%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20they%20would%20resume%20them%20until%20Israel%20lifts%20its%20blockade%20of%20aid%20to%20the%20shattered%20Palestinian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20statement%20did%20not%20reference%20the%20dispute%20over%20Israel%2C%20but%20focused%20on%20previous%20Houthi%20attacks%20on%20merchant%20shipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20all%20Houthi%20terrorists%2C%20YOUR%20TIME%20IS%20UP%2C%20AND%20YOUR%20ATTACKS%20MUST%20STOP%2C%20STARTING%20TODAY.%20IF%20THEY%20DON'T%2C%20HELL%20WILL%20RAIN%20DOWN%20UPON%20YOU%20LIKE%20NOTHING%20YOU%20HAVE%20EVER%20SEEN%20BEFORE!%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20NOT%20threaten%20the%20American%20People%2C%20their%20President...%20or%20Worldwide%20shipping%20lanes.%20If%20you%20do%2C%20BEWARE%2C%20because%20America%20will%20hold%20you%20fully%20accountable%20and%2C%20we%20won't%20be%20nice%20about%20it!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20United%20States%20reclassified%20the%20Houthi%20movement%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bforeign%20terrorist%20organisation%26quot%3B%2C%20banning%20any%20US%20interaction%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPentagon%20spokesman%20Sean%20Parnell%20said%20the%20Houthis%20had%20%26quot%3Battacked%20US%20warships%20174%20times%20and%20commercial%20vessels%20145%20times%20since%202023%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis%20captured%20Sanaa%20in%202014%20and%20were%20poised%20to%20overrun%20most%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20before%20a%20Saudi-led%20coalition%20intervened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20has%20largely%20been%20on%20hold%20since%20a%202022%20ceasefire%2C%20but%20the%20promised%20peace%20process%20has%20stalle