sla%20and%20SpaceX%20outside%20Delaware%20has%20made%20waves.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EState%20lawmakers%20are%20trying%20to%20maintain%20Delaware%20as%20a%20top%20destination%20for%20business%20incorporation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20generations%2C%20Delaware%20has%20been%20a%20top%20destination%20for%20business%20incorporation%2C%20giving%20the%20First%20State%20an%20outsized%20level%20of%20influence%20relative%20to%20its%20small%20population%20of%20just%20over%20one%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20state%20is%20now%20working%20fervently%20to%20preserve%20its%20business-friendly%20reputation%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20moved%20the%20corporate%20home%20of%20both%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20from%20Delaware%20to%20Texas%20last%20year.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20made%20the%20decision%20after%20a%20Delaware%20judge%20struck%20down%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-strikes-down-elon-musk-tesla-compensation-pay-package-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2455%20billion%20compensation%20package%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Musk.%20Several%20other%20high-profile%20businesses%20followed%20his%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelaware%20lawmakers%20are%20now%20taking%20up%20a%20bill%20that%20seeks%20to%20maintain%20the%20state%20as%20a%20premier%20location%20for%20businesses%20by%20altering%20its%20corporate%20law%20structure.%20The%20bill%2C%20which%20was%20passed%20unanimously%20by%20the%20state%20Senate%20on%20Thursday%2C%20would%20change%20how%20deals%20between%20corporate%20leaders%20and%20major%20shareholders%20are%20handled%20in%20Delaware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Delaware%20House%20of%20Representatives%20will%20take%20up%20the%20bill%20next%2C%20and%20should%20it%20pass%20the%20lower%20chamber%2C%20it%20will%20head%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelaware-governor-matt-meyer-corporate-law-elon-musk-bill-ackman-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDemocratic%20Gov.%20Matt%20Meyer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20supports%20the%20measure.%20Meyer%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20in%20February%20about%20threats%20to%20the%20state's%20corporate%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20is%2C%20Delaware%20is%20the%20best%20location%20in%20the%20world%20for%20a%20company%20to%20incorporate%2C%20and%20that's%20thanks%20to%20our%20legal%20expertise%20dating%20back%20to%201792.%20But%20let's%20be%20clear%3A%20If%20any%20entity%20leaves%20Delaware%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20work%20to%20win%20them%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20governor%2C%20who%20took%20office%20in%20January%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20state%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20Bryan%20Townsend%2C%20the%20bill's%20primary%20sponsor%2C%20told%20Delaware%20Public%20Media%20that%20the%20changes%20are%20not%20intended%20to%20sway%20Musk%20to%20return%20but%20to%20ensure%20that%20companies%20considering%20leaving%20the%20state%20do%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20there%20to%20be%20no%20guardrails%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20what%20other%20states%20might%20be%20offering%2C%26quot%3B%20Townsend%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20important%20guardrails%2C%20but%20they've%20got%20to%20be%20predictable%20and%20consistent%20and%20workable%20out%20there%20in%20terms%20of%20all%20the%20kinds%20of%20transactions%20that%20companies%20enter%20into.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20bill%20wouldn't%20be%20retroactive%2C%20meaning%20it%20wouldn't%20affect%20the%20proceedings%20involving%20Musk%2C%20the%20Tesla%20CEO's%20ongoing%20situation%20could%20have%20major%20implications%20for%20Delaware's%20business%20climate%20moving%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202024%2C%20Musk%20took%20to%20X%20to%20criticize%20the%20state%20after%20Chancery%20Court%20Judge%20Kathaleen%20McCormick%20blocked%20his%20compensation%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNever%20incorpo