20ride%20at%20Disney%20World%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d1cb1cb8b41a9673fa6d9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERiding%20a%20vintage%20Disney%20ride%2C%20the%20Astro%20Orbiter%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20with%20my%20grandson%20was%20memorable.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20the%20same%20day%20Astro%20Orbiter%20was%20going%20down%20for%20a%20refurbishment.%20We%20met%20a%20few%20Cast%20Members%20in%20line%20that%20were%20getting%20their%20last%20rides%20in%20before%20it%20closed%20until%20summer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228648ddfa-9bc8-4bcb-922e-c253387e3cd4%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisney%20magic%20stopped%20the%20toddler%20meltdown%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20our%20planning%2C%20we%20gave%20the%20parents%20a%20date%20night.%20We%20planned%20to%20see%20my%20grandma's%20favorite%20Country%20Bears%20with%20the%20little%20one.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%2C%20we%20had%20a%20passed-out%20cold%20toddler%20in%20a%20stroller%20for%20a%20few%20hours.%20After%20some%20cheeseburger%20eggrolls%2C%20we%20staked%20out%20our%20spot%20at%20Magic%20Kingdom%20for%20the%20nighttime%20show%20Happily%20Ever%20After.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Family%20possing%20for%20photo%20at%20Disney%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d1cbf8b8b41a9673fa6dcc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225568%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Disney%20PhotoPass%20photographer%20gave%20us%20this%20photo%20idea%3Cp%3EDisney%20PhotoPass%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20he%20woke%20up%20to%20us%20instead%20of%20Mom%20and%20Dad%2C%20he%20had%20a%20meltdown.%20It%20had%20been%20a%20long%20day%2C%20and%20he%20was%20just%20having%20none%20of%20it.%20We%20considered%20leaving%20as%20the%20screaming%20got%20even%20louder.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20those%20famous%20first%20few%20bars%20of%20the%20show%20music%20started%2C%20and%20instantly%2C%20the%20crying%20stopped.%20For%20the%20next%2018%20minutes%2C%20Disney%20magic%20took%20over.%20And%20thankfully%2C%20it%20was%20long%20enough%20for%20Mom%20and%20Dad%20to%20make%20it%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b27e9718-44ec-45e1-9162-c98ad23c7af9%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20made%20so%20many%20memories%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20made%20so%20many%20magical%20memories%20over%20our%203.5%20days%20of%20grandparenting%20at%20Disney%20World.%20One%20we%20are%20all%20still%20laughing%20about%20happened%20on%20our%20last%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20out-of-this-world%20drinks%20and%20snacks%20at%20Oga's%20Cantina%20we%20saw%20the%20wait%20time%20for%20Millennium%20Falcon%3A%20Smuggler's%20Run%20was%20only%2015%20minutes.%20Spontaneous%20decision%20made!%20Not%20only%20did%20we%20all%20get%20to%20sit%20together%2C%20but%20we%20also%20had%20a%20job%20to%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGrandpa%20and%20Nonna%20were%20pilots%2C%20and%20my%20grandson%20was%20an%20engineer.%20All%20four%20adults%20got%20super%20into%20the%20ride%2C%20laughing%2C%20yelling%20instructions%20at%20each%20other%2C%20and%20trying%20to%20help%20my%20grandson%20when%20it%20was%20his%20turn.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20didn't%20do%20well%20and%20crashed%20the%20spaceship%20a%20few%20times.%20At%20dinner%2C%20my%20grandson%20looked%20at%20me%20and%20very%20seriously%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNonna%20crashed%20the%20spaceship.%20Why%20did%20you%20do%20that%2C%20Nonna%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20then%20proceeded%20to%20tell%20our%20waiter%20and%20just%20about%20anyone%20who%20would%20listen%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20trip%20and%20once%20we%20were%20home%20how%20I%20crashed%20the%20spaceship%20so%20he%20couldn't%20push%20the%20button.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20time%20I've%20seen%20him%20since%20he%20asks%20me%20why%20I%20crashed%20the%20spaceship.%20Fireworks%2C%20hugging%20Tigger%2C%20riding%20his%20first%20roller%20coaster%2C%20and%20it's%20that%20I%20crashed%20the%20spaceship%20he%20remembers.%20And%20I%20love%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaking-grandchild-to-disney-world-first-time-discoveries-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742077981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d1cd8e69253ccddf9907e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaking-grandchild-to-disney-world-first-time-discoveries-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I've%20been%20to%20Disney%20World%2020%20times%2C%20and%20the%20last%20time%20we%20took%20our%20grandson%20with%20us.%20I%20discovered%20new%20rides%20and%20details%20seeing%20the%20park%20through%20his%20eyes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Trisha%20Daab)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A226%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaking-grandchild-to-disney-world-first-time-discoveries-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20tornadoes%3A%20Extreme%20weather%20leaves%20trail%20of%20destruction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742077447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fdafc%2Flive%2Fea089a20-01eb-11f0-b50e-9d086302645f.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fce8m252ye8mo%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2020%20people%20have%20died%20after%20tornadoes%20and%20severe%20storms%20tore%20through%20central%20and%20southern%20states.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22