ublic%20-%20and%20the%20sisters%20of%20the%20Pious%20Disciples%20of%20the%20Divine%20Master%20make%20sure%20all%20who%20call%20it%20get%20a%20real%20person%2C%20not%20the%20%26quot%3Bpress%201%20for%20English%2C%202%20for%20Latin%26quot%3B%20version%20of%20the%20automation%20that's%20become%20the%20norm%20at%20major%20institutions%20and%20businesses%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20Vatican's%20voice%20-%20a%20voice%20that%20despite%20the%20digitalisation%20of%20communications%2C%20the%20Vatican%20wants%20to%20preserve%20as%20a%20human%20voice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mother%20Micaela%2C%20the%20order's%20mother%20superior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pious%20Disciples%20sisters%20are%20part%20of%20the%20100-year-old%20Pauline%20orders%2C%20which%20are%20focused%20on%20communications%2C%20including%20landmark%20Catholic%20publishing%20operations%20around%20the%20world.%20In%20spring%201970%2C%20they%20were%20called%20to%20operate%20the%20Vatican%20switchboard%20and%20instructed%20by%20the%20then-mother%20superior%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20voice%20that%20does%20good%20because%20through%20the%20phone%20wire%20it%20communicates%20Christ%20himself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20often%20with%20headsets%20over%20their%20veils%2C%20the%20sisters%20cover%20the%20phones%20for%2012%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20seven%20days%20a%20week%2C%20in%20front%20of%20large%20monitors%20that%20show%20the%20incoming%20call's%20country%20of%20origin.%20Gendarmes%2C%20the%20Vatican's%20police%2C%20take%20the%20night%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20dozen%20sisters%20hailing%20from%20Italy%2C%20the%20Philippines%2C%20Poland%20and%20elsewhere%20take%20calls%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20predominantly%20in%20Italian%2C%20English%20and%20Spanish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20callers%20just%20need%20to%20be%20directed%20to%20the%20right%20Vatican%20office%20or%20official%2C%20and%20the%20sisters%20oblige%20with%20the%20aid%20of%20massive%20yearbooks%20and%20direc