to%20children.%20The%20coordinated%20lawsuits%20resemble%20the%20strategy%20used%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-lawsuits-mirror-tobacco-purdue-pharma-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etake%20down%20Big%20Tobacco%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Purdue%20Pharma%2C%20putting%20TikTok%20in%20some%20unsavory%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJayne%20Conroy%2C%20an%20attorney%20at%20a%20firm%20that%20represents%20some%2050%20plaintiffs%20in%20a%20separate%20class-action%20lawsuit%20accusing%20social%20media%20platforms%20of%20harming%20children%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-lawsuit-algorithm-children-internal-documents-revealed-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estate%20investigations%20into%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20it%20is%20designed%20to%20%26quot%3Brelentlessly%20engage%20and%20exploit%20the%20adolescent%20brain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAriana%20Hoet%2C%20the%20executive%20clinical%20director%20at%20the%20Kids%20Mental%20Health%20Foundation%2C%20said%20children%20who%20spend%20several%20hours%20a%20day%20on%20social%20media%20are%20at%20an%20increased%20risk%20for%20mental%20health%20conditions%20like%20anxiety%20and%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20said%20the%20impact%20social%20media%20has%20on%20children%20depends%20on%20how%20much%20time%20they%20spend%20scrolling%20online%2C%20what%20they%20look%20at%2C%20and%20with%20whom%20they%20engage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20we%20always%20recommend%20is%20making%20sure%20that%20the%20parents%20are%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoet%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20decide%20to%20give%20access%20to%20your%20child%2C%20you%20want%20to%20continue%20monitoring%2C%20you%20want%20to%20continue%20conversations%2C%20and%20then%20you%20want%20to%20teach%20them%20digital%20literacy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoet%20said%20it's%20important%20for%20parents%20to%20monitor%20their%20children's%20social%20media%20activity%2C%20especially%20given%20that%20children's%20brains%20aren't%20yet%20fully%20developed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20as%20adults%20with%20fully%20formed%20brains%2C%20we%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20disengaging%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoet%20said.%20%26quot%3BKids%20are%20never%20going%20to%20win.%20There's%20no%20way%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20beat%20out%20these%20algorithms%20that%20are%20created%20to%20keep%20them%20on%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20has%20denied%20accusations%20that%20it%20is%20addictive%20to%20children%2C%20but%20has%20nonetheless%20added%20features%20like%20default%20screentime%20limits%2C%20family%20pairing%2C%20and%20default%20private%20accounts%20for%20children%20under%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20has%20also%20added%20a%20%26quot%3Bwind%20down%26quot%3B%20feature%20for%20teen%20accounts.%20After%2010%20p.m.%2C%20a%20pop-up%20will%20encourage%20teens%20to%20log%20off%20for%20the%20night%20with%20%26quot%3Bcalming%20music.%26quot%3B%20The%20pop-ups%20are%20optional%2C%20however%2C%20and%20the%20teen%20can%20continue%20using%20TikTok%20after%20dismissing%20them.%20TikTok%20also%20says%20it%20will%20add%20%26quot%3Bmeditation%20exercises%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20wind-down%20prompts%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20wind-down%20and%20meditation%20features%20seemed%20like%20surface-level%20fixes%20that%20do%20not%20address%20the%20root%20of%20the%20issue%3A%20that%20social%20media%20content%20is%20addictive%20to%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20child%20or%20adult%20is%20going%20to%20opt%20into%20meditating%20within%20an%20app%20that%20succeeds%20at%20delivering%20the%20most%20viral%2C%20engaging%20content%20that's%20personalized%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20I%20want%20to%20do%3F%20Do%20I%20want%20to%20meditate%3F%20Or%20do%20I%20want%20to%20keep%20consuming%20this%20addictive%20content%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22772d93b0-bab2-4633-9450-c37ea0079886%5C%22%3EWho%20is%20responsible%20for%20a%20child's%20mental%20health%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOmar%20Gudi%C3%B1o%2C%20the%20deputy%20clinical%20director%20and%20senior%20psychologist%20at%20the%20Child%20Mind%20Institute%2C%20said%20the%20parental%20controls%20are%20a%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20complex%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Gudi%C3%B1o%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20also%20want%20to%20be%20thinking%20about%20what%20messages%20we%20are%20sending%20at%20a%20family%20level%20and%20what%20messages%20we%20are%20sending%20in%20schools%2C%20so%20there's%20multiple%20points%20for%20interventions.%20There's%20probably%20more%20that%20apps%20can%20be%20doing%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoet%20said%20the%20onus%20for%20protecting%20young%20social%20media%20users'%20mental%20health%20typically%20falls%20on%20the%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20those%20burden%20falls%20on%20parents%2C%20and%20that's%20unfair%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoet%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20the%20tech%20companies%20to%20be%20more%20responsible%20in%20their%20design%2C%20and%20we%20need%20them%20to%20be%20more%20responsible%20in%20sharing%20the%20data%20that%20shows%20how%20it's%20impacting%20kids.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoliticians%20also%20need%20to%20step%20up%20and%20create%20laws%20focused%20on%20protecting%20children's%20mental%20health%20during%20the%20digital%20age%2C%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20at%20a%20place%20where%20the%20technology%20developed%20fast%20and%20we're%20catching%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGudi%C3%B1o%20said%20tech%20companies%20designing%20social%20media%20apps%20with%20young%20audiences%20in%20mind%20could%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20apps%20could%20do%20more%20to%20think%20about%20what%20content%20kids%20are%20exposed%20to%20or%20how%20the%20app%20is%20set%20up%20to%20keep%20them%20on%20for%20longer%2C%20there%20might%20be%20more%20to%20be%20done%20to%20help%20bring%20the%20risk%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGudi%C3%B1o%20said%20designing%20apps%20that%20balance%20children's%20mental%20health%20and%20social%20media's%20quest%20for%20user%20engagement%20might%20seem%20%26quot%3Bincompatible%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20challenge%20presents%20an%20opportunity%20for%20tech%20companies%20and%20families%20to%20work%20toward%20a%20common%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20best%20for%20children's%20development%3F%20How%20do%20we%20design%20content%20and%20set%20up%20families%20for%20success%20in%20a%20way%20that's%20going%20to%20work%20for%20everyone%3F%26quot%3B%20Gudi%C3%B1o%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-mental-health-addiction-parental-controls-children-lawsuits-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742061014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d2152e585f1dff88b1fa2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-mental-health-addiction-parental-controls-children-lawsuits-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TikTok's%20new%20child%20safety%20features%20increase%20parental%20control%2C%20but%20they%20are%20easily%20bypassed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer%2CLauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-mental-health-addiction-parental-controls-children-lawsuits-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rosmerta%20Digital%20seeks%20insolvency%20proceedings%20against%20Ola%20Electric's%20arm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742060980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frosmerta-digital-se