the%20home%20secretary%2C%20secretary%20of%20legislative%20department%2C%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20Unique%20Identification%20Authority%20of%20India%20(UIDAI)%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20is%20taking%20proactive%20and%20definitive%20steps%20to%20resolve%20legacy%20issues%20which%20have%20been%20pending%20for%20decades%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20has%20not%20completed%20even%20a%20month%20since%20taking%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20the%20new%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20is%20looking%20to%20resolve%20the%20duplicate%20voter%20ID%20card%20issue%20which%20has%20been%20pending%20for%20nearly%2025%20years%20in%20the%20next%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commissioner%20will%20be%20conducting%20all-party%20meetings%20at%20the%20levels%20of%20electoral%20registration%20officers%20(EROs)%2C%20district%20election%20officers%20(DEOs)%2C%20and%20chief%20electoral%20officers%20(CEOs)%20before%20March%2031%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20Mr%20Kumar%20will%20seek%20suggestions%20from%20all%20national%20and%20state%20parties%20within%20the%20legal%20framework%20by%20April%2030%2C%20which%20would%20be%20an%20exercise%20done%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EField-level%20political%20agents%20including%20booth-level%20agents%2C%20polling%20agents%2C%20counting%20agents%2C%20and%20election%20agents%20will%20be%20trained%20about%20their%20key%20roles%20as%20per%20a%20legal%20framework%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20all%20Indians%20who%20are%20over%2018%20years%20old%20should%20be%20able%20to%20vote%2C%20and%20linking%20Aadhaar%20with%20EPIC%20is%20one%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlagging%20alleged%20cases%20of%20duplicate%20voter%20card%20numbers%20allocated%20to%20people%20in%20different%20states%2C%20the%20Opposition%20Trinamool%20Congress%20alleged%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20been%20fudging%20the%20voters'%20lists%20to%20help%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20also%20made%20similar%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20allows%20voluntary%20seeding%20of%20voter%20rolls%20with%20the%20Aadhaar%20database.%20The%20government%20told%20parliament%20the%20Aadhaar%20and%20voter%20card%20linking%20exercise%20was%20%26quot%3Bprocess%20driven%26quot%3B%20and%20no%20target%20or%20timelines%20have%20been%20given%20for%20the%20proposed%20linking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20said%20the%20names%20of%20those%20who%20do%20not%20link%20their%20Aadhaar%20with%20EPIC%20will%20not%20be%20struck%20off%20the%20electoral%20rolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrinamool%20Reacts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20reports%20of%20the%20meeting%20called%20by%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20came%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20jumped%20in%20with%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20EC%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bface-saving%20measure%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20leader%20Sagarika%20Ghose%20said%20the%20statements%20issued%20by%20the%20ECI%20over%20duplicate%20EPIC%20numbers%20and%20the%20meeting%20being%20called%20now%20are%20%26quot%3Bface-saving%20measures%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20three%20statements.%20Now%20this%20meeting.%20This%20is%20just%20a%20face-saving%20measure.%20We%20will%20keep%20a%20hawk-eye%20vigil%20till%20the%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Ghose%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2011%2C%20a%2010-member%20Trinamool%20delegation%20met%20the%20full%20Election%20Commission%20bench%20over%20the%20duplicate%20EPIC%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duplication%20of%20voter%20ID%20card%20numbers%20in%20different%20states%20was%20raised%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20on%20February%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20on%20March%202%20in%20a%20statement%